<span id="Introduction"></span>
== Einleitung ==

[[File:LinkGroup.svg|32px]]

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
An [[App_LinkGroup|App LinkGroup]], or formally an {{incode|App::LinkGroup}}, is a type of object that can act as a container for other objects and has a placement. Similarly to an [[App_Part|App Part]], but without scope restrictions and with additional features to control how elements are removed and added to it.
</div>

